nodes.text: Mus Kat & Nalpak were a band known for the song "Black Spire Harvest," which was played at Oga's Cantina in Black Spire Outpost on Batuu. Other songs performed by Mus Kat & Nalpak included "Bright Suns," "Doshka," and "Turbulence," all of which were also played at the cantina by the droid R-3X.
